commentPostTextItems.html: Thats the end of the match here at SuperSport Park, Centurion Australia win this by 96 runs
Valiant run-chase from the Sri Lankan batsmen, but 319 was always going to be imposing
The Australian batted well to put up the score of 319, ponting was the hero with 114 and Gilchrist (99) played their part well
Fernando grabs 3 wickets for 47 runs yet another classic bowling display by the Australians bowlers
. de Silva played a good innings today - made 92 off 94 balls lee ended the day with 3 wickets, 2 for McGrath and Hogg
Ricky Ponting is Man of the Match
that concludes our coverage of today's match at SuperSport Park,Centurion, we hope you enjoyed it

We have enjoyed bringing this game and hope you will enjoy tomorrows game between Zimbabwe and New Zealand.  Until then, its bye bye from all of us here at CricInfo.com any comments about today's coverage can be sent to
comms@cricinfo.com - all feedback is greatly appreciated

stories.title: Ponting and Lee star in emphatic Australia win
stories.summary:
A century from skipper Ricky Ponting and devastating spell of express pace
bowling from speedster Brett Lee handed Australia an emphatic 96 run victory
in their opening Super Six clash against Sri Lanka at Centurion on Friday
